---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from "../consts";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">
				Enabling Safe AI Development Through Extended Hardware Security
			</h1>

			<p class="mb-8">
				Modern AI development demands new approaches to security and
				verification. We're extending existing hardware security
				infrastructure to enable automated, privacy-preserving
				verification of compute workloads - creating immediate benefits
				for cloud providers while building toward safer AI development.
			</p>

			<section class="mb-12">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Immediate Impact</h2>
				<p>
					Cloud service providers face growing challenges in verifying
					AI workloads while protecting customer privacy. Our approach
					enables:
				</p>
				<ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
					<li>Automated pre-compute verification</li>
					<li>Privacy-preserving auditing</li>
					<li>Scalable trust mechanisms</li>
					<li>Integration with existing infrastructure</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-12">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
					Building on Proven Foundations
				</h2>
				<p>
					Rather than creating entirely new systems, we're extending
					battle-tested hardware security infrastructure:
				</p>
				<ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
					<li>Industry standard secure enclaves</li>
					<li>Established attestation protocols</li>
					<li>Existing confidential computing frameworks</li>
					<li>Proven supply chain security measures</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-12">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Join Our Effort</h2>
				<p>
					We're looking for partners and team members across multiple
					domains:
				</p>

				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-3">Team Roles</h3>
				<ul class="list-disc ml-6">
					<li>
						Standards Development Lead: Drive engagement with
						hardware security standards bodies and industry working
						groups
					</li>
					<li>
						Security Architecture Engineer: Design
						privacy-preserving verification protocols
					</li>
					<li>
						ML Verification Researcher: Develop pre-compute
						verification methods
					</li>
					<li>
						Hardware Security Expert: Integrate with existing
						security infrastructure
					</li>
					<li>
						Policy & Standards Specialist: Guide standards evolution
						and industry adoption
					</li>
				</ul>

				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-3">
					Partnership Opportunities
				</h3>
				<ul class="list-disc ml-6">
					<li>
						Security IP Vendors: Integrate verification capabilities
					</li>
					<li>
						Verification Services: Develop white-box security
						auditing
					</li>
					<li>
						ML Research Groups: Advance pre-training verification
						methods
					</li>
					<li>
						Manufacturing Partners: Explore advanced security
						implementations
					</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-12">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Funding & Support</h2>
				<p>We're seeking support to accelerate:</p>
				<ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
					<li>Standards development and adoption</li>
					<li>Reference implementations</li>
					<li>Industry integration programs</li>
					<li>Research into advanced verification methods</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-12">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Learn More</h2>
				<p>Explore our detailed blog series:</p>
				<ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
					<li>
						<a href="/blog/1-hardware-security-standards" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">
							Extending Hardware Security Standards for Safe AI Development
						</a>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a href="/blog/2-privacy-preserving" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">
							Privacy-Preserving Compute Auditing for Cloud Providers
						</a>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a href="/blog/3-hardware-implementation" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">
							Evolving Hardware Security: From Standards to Implementation
						</a>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a href="/blog/4-technical-impl-paths" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">
							Technical Implementation Paths for Safe AI Hardware
						</a>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-12">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
				<p class="mb-4">
					We're excited to collaborate with partners and welcome inquiries from potential team members. Reach out to discuss:
					<a
						href="mailto:team@earendil.ai"
						class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors"
					>
							team@earendil.ai
				</a>
				</p>

			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
